seo: 万户OA,SQL注入漏洞,showResult.action,后台漏洞
summary: 该插件用于检测万户OA系统中showResult.action接口的SQL注入漏洞，攻击者可能通过此漏洞获取数据库敏感信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the showResult.action interface of Whu OA system. Attackers may obtain sensitive database information through this vulnerability.
